  <brief_title>β Blocker Use and Mortality in Hospital Survivors of Acute Myocardial Infarction Without Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>β Blocker Use and Mortality in Hospital Survivors of Acute Myocardial Infarction Without Heart Failure</official_title>
